title: Incredible Edible America with the Dunhams
overview: In Incredible Edible America with the Dunhams, comedian Jeff Dunham and his wife, Audrey, take viewers on a food tour of the nation, seeking America's most unbelievable eats, including a $777 burger, ice cream served in a doughnut cone, and a 27-inch cheesesteak piled high with everything but the kitchen sink. Jeff and Audrey will celebrate America's culinary awesomeness and meet the masterminds behind these incredible eats!
